title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Keno' game
maintext:

(two, three, four, five, eleven, thirteen, twenty-one, twenty-eight, thirty-six, forty-three, forty-eight, fifty, fifty-one, fifty-six, fifty-eight, sixty, sixty-six, sixty-seven, seventy, seventy-one, seventy-nine, eighty)
